sql:
SELECT title, director, 
       LEAD(director) OVER (ORDER BY release_date) AS next_director
FROM films;

external_knowledge:
- 'well-liked by audiences' refers to films with an average rating greater than 4 out of 5;
- 'financial success' is indicated by the total gross revenue of the films within each genre;
- The question is seeking information on genres with positive financial and critical reception.
